===Noun===
'''{{ARchar|ذُو الحِجّةِ}}''' {{IPAchar|(ðu l-ħíjja)}} {{m}}

#[[Dhul Hijjah]], the twelfth and last of the twelve months of the Muslim lunar calendar, each beginning with a [[new moon]]. [[Dhul Hijjah]] means "lord of the pilgrimage" in Arabic, and this is when pilgrims visit [[Mecca]].

